      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Frost Bites",
        "Client": "Stranded Safari Member",
        "Description": "Help us! HELP US! Anyone! Our\r\nsafari has been surrounded by\r\nmonsters, and now we\u0027re stuck out\r\nin the cold! Good thing I wore some-\r\nthing warm and I\u0027ll give you some\r\nmaterials to make your very own\r\nif you get those monsters to scram! ",
        "Target": "Hunt a Lagombi, a Barioth,\r\nand a Goss Harag",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "\u00C7a fait froid dans le dos",
        "Client": "Touriste en safari",
        "Description": "\u00C0 l\u0027aide ! Au secours ! Notre\r\nsafari a \u00E9t\u00E9 interrompu par\r\ndes monstres, et on est coinc\u00E9s\r\nici avec ce froid ! Heureusement\r\nque j\u0027ai de bons habits !\r\nD\u00E9barrasse-toi de ces monstres et\r\nt\u0027auras de quoi faire les m\u00EAmes ! ",
        "Target": "Chasser un Lagombi, un Barioth\r\net un Goss Harag",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Morsi di ghiaccio",
        "Client": "Safarista bloccato",
        "Description": "Aiuto! AIUTO! C\u0027\u00E8 nessuno? I\r\nmostri hanno circondato il\r\nnostro safari e siamo bloccati\r\nal freddo! Almeno indosso abiti\r\ncaldi. Potrai crearli anche tu\r\ncon i materiali che ti dar\u00F2 se\r\nfarai smammare questi mostri! ",
        "Target": "Caccia un Lagombi, un Barioth\r\ne un Goss Harag",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Frostbeulen",
        "Client": "Safari-Mitglied in Not",
        "Description": "Hilfe! HILFE! Unsere Safari\r\nwurde von Monstern umzingelt\r\nund wir sitzen in der K\u00E4lte\r\nfest! Zum Gl\u00FCck hab ich warme\r\nKleider! Vertreib die Monster,\r\ndann geb ich dir Materialien\r\nf\u00FCr warme Kleidung! ",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Lagombi, einen Barioth und\r\neinen Goss Harag.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Mordiscos heladores",
        "Client": "Miembro del safari",
        "Description": "\u00A1Auxorro! \u00A1Soquilio!\r\n\u00A1Unos monstruos nos han\r\nrodeado estando de safari!\r\nMenos mal que llevo ropa de\r\nabrigo. Si nos ayudas, te doy\r\nalgunos materiales para que\r\nt\u00FA tambi\u00E9n te hagas algo. ",
